			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Be prepared to put in some hours camping for PBBs. I spent two full nights camping these evil eyes, Lords and such (never met the King, two Lord Soptyvr visits). As a level 39 magician, it was no prob, I was basically killing them as fast as they could spawn. And there was pretty much no one else in the zone while I was camping, so competition for the spawn point was nil. <BR>
<BR>
I counted, and I killed a total of 53 evil eye Lords and 49 evil eyes. On the 99th kill, I got my first PBB. Got my second on the last kill. Not exactly 1 in 20 for me, d'oh! <BR>
<BR>
Anyway, the other loot wasn't too bad. From the last forty or so kills, when I was keeping track of loot, got 5 topazes, 16 evil eye stalks (poison component), 3 optic nerves, some words, runes and misc treasure. Probably made 150-200pp all in all. <BR>
<BR>
Just don't count on stopping by and getting those polished bone bracers in a half an hour.<BR>
<BR>
Good hunting,<BR>
Matk the Magician (39th) &lt;Rising Dragon&gt; The Seventh Hammer
